description: These simple hand rolls are the quickest way to get your homemade sushi fix.
name: Salmon Temaki Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Cook the rice according to pack instructions, tip into a bowl and mix with half of the rice wine vinegar.
Whisk the soy sauce, remaining rice wine vinegar and chilli in a small bowl to make a dressing.

Cut the nori sheets in half diagonally to make 8 triangles. Divide the rice between the triangles, leaving a border at the edges. Place the vegetables and smoked salmon on top of the rice and roll up to form a cone shape.
Serve the temaki with dipping sauce and pickled ginger.
